title: 12/16/2020 - Best of The Herd
itunes:title: 12/16/2020 - Best of The Herd
description:
-Colin has no issue with how the committee ranks non-power 5 teams

-The NBA might have been better off if Giannis had left Milwaukee

-James Harden is a scorer, not a leader

-Browns fans are desperate to validate Baker Mayfield but he's not special

-Aaron Rodgers wants you to think he's in some GOAT conversations, he's not


Guest: Nick Wright, FS1's 'First Things First'
